HTTP Router
###########

.. _description:

**http-router** -- A simple router for HTTP applications

.. _badges:

.. image:: https://github.com/klen/http-router/workflows/tests/badge.svg
    :target: https://github.com/klen/http-router/actions
    :alt: Tests Status

